ZH: 我们去公园散步。
EN: We went to the park for a walk.

ZH: 这座城市有很多美丽的花园。
EN: This city has many beautiful gardens.

ZH: 她在园里种了许多蔬菜和水果。
EN: She planted a lot of vegetables and fruits in the garden.

ZH: 春天是去公园的好时候。
EN: Spring is a good time to go to the park.

ZH: 这个园里有一座漂亮的喷泉。
EN: There is a beautiful fountain in this garden.

ZH: 鸟儿在园里欢快地歌唱。
EN: The birds are singing happily in the garden.

ZH: 绿地公园是我们家附近的一个漂亮的园。
EN: Ludi Park is a beautiful garden near our house.

ZH: 这是一个有着悠久历史的园林。
EN: This is a garden with a long history.

ZH: 园里的玫瑰花开得很美。
EN: The roses in the garden are blooming beautifully.

ZH: 我喜欢在园林中散步。
EN: I like to take a walk in the garden.

ZH: 公园里有很多游乐设施。
EN: There are many amusement facilities in the park.

ZH: 园中的湖水清澈见底。
EN: The lake in the garden is crystal clear.

ZH: 这个园是一个放松心情的好地方。
EN: This garden is a good place to relax.

ZH: 园里的树木参天。
EN: The trees in the garden are very tall.

ZH: 我们组织了一次园游会。
EN: We organized a garden party.

ZH: 园里的草坪很适合野餐。
EN: The lawn in the garden is perfect for a picnic.

ZH: 雨后的园林更加清新美丽。
EN: The garden looks fresher and more beautiful after the rain.

ZH: 园中的凉亭很适合休息。
EN: The pavilion in the garden is perfect for resting.

ZH: 我们在花园中举行了一场庆祝活动。
EN: We held a celebration event in the garden.

ZH: 园林景色的美丽让人心旷神怡。
EN: The beauty of the garden landscape is refreshing to the soul.
